# Self-Review Checklist

Before submitting or committing, agent must:
1. Run lint and formatter (e.g. `npm run lint && npm run format`).  
2. Execute tests (`npm test` or `pytest`).  
3. Confirm no TODO/FIXME comments remain.  
4. Verify that all new functions have docstrings or JSDoc.  
5. Summarize changes in a brief bullet list.
